data.description: Welcome to this charming 3 bedroom 2.5 bath traditional home in the highly sought-after community, The Terraces at Union Pointe subdivision, ideally near downtown Union City! This lovely home boasts a spacious, open floor plan, perfect for entertaining guests and creating cherished memories with family and loved ones. Upon Foyer entry, you'll be greeted by a bright, airy living room with soaring vaulted ceilings, providing the perfect ambiance for relaxation and unwinding after a long day. The adjacent dining area flows seamlessly into the kitchen, which features stained cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The primary suite is a true oasis, featuring a walk-in closet and a private en-suite bathroom. Two additional bedrooms offer plenty of space for guests, a growing family, and a full bathroom. Other features of this lovely home include a half bathroom on the main floor, a two-car garage, a laundry room, and a back patio. This home is just minutes away from shopping, dining, entertainment options, schools, and easy access to major highways for a quick commute.
